               <msContents>
                  <summary change="#add-summary">
                     1 copy of The Divan of Hafiz followed by the Pandnamah attributed to Sa'di and with the Bustan of Sa'di written diagonally in the margins by 2 authors
                  </summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="RAS_Persian_275-item1">
                     <author key="person_56731778" ref="http://viaf.org/viaf/56731778/">
                        <persName xml:lang="fa-Latn-x-lc" type="standard">Ḥāfiẓ, 14th cent.</persName>
